 ### arrays_and_strings – programs based on list and string operations ###

  largest_smallest.py → Find biggest and smallest number in a list

  count_even_odd.py → Count how many numbers are even and odd

  string_palindrome.py → Check if a word is the same forward and backward

  vowels_consonants.py → Count vowels and consonants in a word

  sum_of_list.py → Add all numbers in a list

  list_statistics.py → Find total, average, max, and min in a list
